estCompileOnly \"com.google.protobuf:protobuf-java:$libraryVersion\"` from:\n  - `tests/src/com.google.protobuf/protobuf-javalite/3.25.3/build.gradle`\n- Updated `ExtensionSchemasTest` to avoid compile-time references to full-runtime classes:\n  - It now loads `com.google.protobuf.DescriptorProtos$MessageOptions` by class name at runtime, using the existing `testRuntimeOnly` dependency.\n- Added native-image test metadata for that dynamically loaded class:\n  - `tests/src/com.google.protobuf/protobuf-javalite/3.25.3/src/test/resources/META-INF/native-image/reachability-metadata.json`\n\nI also validated the edited JSON syntax. Per instruction, I did not run the Gradle test command locally.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e1f06aed1af2bae0169f902901ce4819d9f210eaf165a6928\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1058, "output": 1057, "cacheRead": 41984, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 44099, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777926785188, "responseId": "resp_0e1f06aed1af2bae0169f90281fb74819d845b246ef6893d87"}, "toolResults": []}
